Suggests: viridis, RColorBrewer, covr, knitr, rmarkdown, tinytest
Depends: R (>= 3.2.0)
Imports: ggplot2, grid, scales, plyr
RoxygenNote: 6.1.1
VignetteBuilder: knitr
